<item>
            <title>[SYNAPSE-488] Dynamic Load Balancing with the DynamicLoadbalanceEndpoint Does not work</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SYNAPSE-488</link>
                <project id="12310201" key="SYNAPSE">Synapse</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The service requests from the clients get properly distributed among the dynamic members. But the responses coming back from them are not routed back to the original client. Client will wait until it finally times out without getting the response.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Steps to reproduce the issue:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Setup the environment for sample 57 (dynamic load balance)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Invoke the client as specified in the documentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
